00:25:43.440 --> 00:25:46.659
But also we can
play with the sound.

00:25:46.659 --> 00:25:48.450
Once you hit a note on
the guitar or piano,

00:25:48.450 --> 00:25:49.940
you're kind of
done on the volume.

00:25:49.940 --> 00:25:54.690
But on accordion, [NOTES]
you can manipulate the sound

00:25:54.690 --> 00:25:55.680
constantly.

00:25:55.680 --> 00:25:57.290
It's also portable,
which is nice.

00:25:57.290 --> 00:26:00.667
