It must go above.

00:26:04.960 --> 00:26:07.300
It cannot go below, obviously.

00:26:07.300 --> 00:26:09.150
But it's just an
amazing instrument.

00:26:09.150 --> 00:26:12.930
It's known around the world to
play so many different genres.

00:26:12.930 --> 00:26:16.320
I do literally play
techno at college parties.

00:26:16.320 --> 00:26:18.180
But then the next day
